By Representative Frost of Auburn, a petition (accompanied by bill, House, No. 1504) of Paul K.
Frost, David F. DeCoste and Joseph D. McKenna relative to the inclusion of mobile homes in the
definition of affordable housing. Housing.
The Commonwealth of Massachusetts
_______________
In the One Hundred and Ninety-Fourth General Court
(2025-2026)
_______________
An Act relative to mobile homes as affordable housing.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Notwithstanding any general or special law to the contrary, all mobile
2 homes shall qualify as affordable housing as defined by Chapter 40B of the General Laws.
